    	<script>
		function getSabavisionNativeRow () {
            var zone, zoneDark;
            if(window.innerWidth <= 670) {
	            zone = '<div id="sabavision_zone_7226-Z103_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
                zoneDark = ' <div id="sabavision_zone_7516-Z589_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
            } else if (window.innerWidth >= 1592){
                zone = '<div id="sabavision_zone_7515-Z992_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
                zoneDark = '<div id="sabavision_zone_7805-Z468_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
            } else {
                zone = '<div id="sabavision_zone_7514-Z566_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
                zoneDark = '<div id="sabavision_zone_7517-Z747_plate" class="w-100"></div>';
            }
            var row = $(document.body).hasClass('theme-dark') ? zoneDark : zone;
            $('#listAdRow').html('<div class="list-wrapper"><section class="list-content">' + row + '</section></div>');
            var adST = setTimeout(function () {
                if (typeof Dox !== "undefined") {
                    Dox.initialize();
                    clearTimeout(adST);
                }
            }, 500);
		}
        $(document).ready(getSabavisionNativeRow);
	</script>
